&lt;p&gt;(% gallery name=sliders %)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;home-welcome&quot;&gt;
	&lt;h1 class=&quot;col-md-12&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;margin-top:0px;padding:15px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Welcome to Gateway Clinics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;h4 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#e30525; color:#fff; padding:10px&quot;&gt;Emergency&amp;nbsp; Contact&amp;nbsp; : &lt;a href=&quot;tel:9245731318&quot; style=&quot;color:#fff !important&quot;&gt;9245731318&lt;/a&gt; / 9042435350 /&amp;nbsp; 0422-2554955/&amp;nbsp; 0422-2542244/&amp;nbsp; 9445961318.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;h3 class=&quot;blinking tab&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;(% gallery name=home-new %)&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Testimonials&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;(% gallery name=tests %)&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&quot;Vijay TV Super Singer Voice expert Mr. Anand Vaidiyanathan met Gateway Hospital Chairman Dr. K. Sendhil Kumar for Conceltation and given his feed back&quot;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://gatewayclinics.com/worlds-heaviest-ovarian-cancer-tumour-news.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;World&#039;s heaviest Ovarian Cancer Tumour weighing 33.5 kg has been removed by Gateway Clinics Doctors&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
	&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Workshop &amp;amp; Conference&lt;/h3&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;(% gallery name=workshop %)&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-12 col-md-12 text-center&quot;&gt;&lt;!--&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Welcome to Gateway Clinics,&lt;/strong&gt; the centre of excellence for the treatment of all gastrointestinal, hepato-biliary, colorectal cancer obesity and other abdominal problems, Established by Dr. K. Senthil Kumar. This centre is situated in the heart of Coimbatore city which is easily accessible by all modes of transportation. Coimbatore was once called as tex-city because of its popular textile industries.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Now the city is very popular for clinics, hospitals, and other medical facilities and hence called as medi-city. Due to its close proximity to the hill stations like Ooty and Kodaikanal and also to &#039;God s Own Country - Kerala&#039; the city is a major destination medical tourism. Our Mission is to provide advanced laparoscopic surgery at affordable cost to all sections of the society. With a mission to reach out, Gateway Clinics has established a centre in chennai at Deepam Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
		--&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;We at &lt;b&gt;Gateway clinics&lt;/b&gt; deliver excellence in patient care with more than 21 years of experience in laparoscopic surgery &amp;amp; Endoscopy. Gateway clinics is equipped with new cutting edge technologies and instruments to help us in our mission. Our philosophy of multi – disciplinary approach to patient care is supported by a state of art Endoscopy unit with the latest technology. As one of the pioneers in “ Day Care Surgery”, patient with diseases of Appendix, Gallbladder, Uterus and&amp;nbsp; Ovaries and problems like inguinal and abdominal hernia , Piles, Fissure and Fistula are sent back home within 24 Hours of Surgery. The main advantages are minimal pain, minimal blood loss and immediate return to normal activity. Numerous latest equipments like High Definition Cameras and Operating Room Suite, Harmonic Scalpel &amp;amp; vessel sealing device help us in our endeavour &amp;amp; add to patient comfort.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Gateway clinics, a speciality clinic focused on the treatment of all Gastro – Intestinal diseases. With a highly skilled and qualified team of doctors, we handle all complex medical and surgical Gastro-intestinal problems and ensure that the patient care is of the highest standard and one of the best in the World.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;data/uploads/pdf/gateway.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;எல்லோருக்கும் இது எச்சரிக்கை.&lt;br /&gt;
			Click To View&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
		&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/articleshow/71145299.cms?utm_source=contentofinterest&amp;amp;utm_medium=text&amp;amp;utm_campaign=cppst&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Gateway Clinics Hospital removes 7kg tumour from woman’s abdomen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
		&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.ndtv.com/tamil-nadu-news/tumour-weighing-7-kg-removed-from-womans-stomach-in-tamil-nadu-2101410?fbclid=IwAR1zzXp7WQKg8FSZbLlz5nUBOHCOSylflHe7OS1JY07RWldW281izDN2kCQ&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Tumour Weighing 7 Kg Removed From Woman&#039;s Stomach In Gateway Clinics, Tamil Nadu&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
		&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.aninews.in/news/national/general-news/tn-doctors-in-coimbatore-remove-7-kg-tumour-from-56-yr-old-womans-stomach20190916042838/#.XX7vwOnwXNw.whatsapp&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Gateway Clinics Doctors in Coimbatore remove 7-kg tumour from 56-yr-old woman&#039;s stomach&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
		&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7UYLWy7CD3g&amp;amp;feature=youtu.be&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Laparoscopic Nissen&#039;s Fundoplication Unedited Live MISCON 2020&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
		&lt;h2&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;best-innovation-paper-award-in-indian-national-surgeons-conference-asicon-2019.html&quot;&gt;Best Innovation paper award in Indian National Surgeon&#039;s conference ASICON 2019&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
